# ─── Deploy notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# • In Vercel → Project → Settings → General: Root Directory must be the repo root
#   (not `src`), or `/api/waitlist` will not deploy.
# • Push latest code, then set variables below on Vercel and redeploy.
# • Confirm FormSubmit’s activation email for your inbox (check spam) once per address.
# • Run: npm run verify:waitlist   (optional: WAITLIST_SMOKE_ORIGIN=https://your-url)

# ─── Local development (`npm run dev`) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Waitlist submits directly to FormSubmit AJAX. Use the same inbox you activate
# at formsubmit.co (see activation email in your spam folder once per address).
VITE_WAITLIST_NOTIFY_EMAIL=

# Optional
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
# VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=

# ─── Vercel (Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables) ───────
# Production & Preview: no VITE_ prefix — used only by Edge function api/waitlist.
#
# WAITLIST_NOTIFY_EMAIL=your-address@gmail.com
#
# Optional — Google Apps Script Web App URL (POST JSON with name, email, persona, source):
# WAITLIST_GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/.../exec
